room_title: Escape room "Alien Escape" by Zoya Escape Rooms in St. Joseph (MI)
room_address: 4298 S Niles Rd, St Joseph, MI 49085
room_description: The evil pharmacist, Dr. Dergun, is up to it once again. World domination is his mission. He was last seen in a cabin in the woods. But the cabin isn’t as simplistic as you might think, it has alien conspiracy written all over it. Your team’s mission is to discover the secrets the cabin holds and to stop Dr. Dergun from taking over the world.
